{"tid":1473143,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"餐廳食肆洗腦大法","createTime":"2019-08-14T18:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T03:32:52.000Z","uid":19944,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0bfe27a80f228dd9cab3e959aa2ef03f48220a58","tid":1473143,"uid":19944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:22:07.000Z","msg":"話說今日小妹去北角福X買糖水，咁啱只得小妹一個顧客，我喺老闆舀完糖水，包裝緊的時候，和老闆對話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老闆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老闆娘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：嘩！少咗咁多人嘅？平時夜晚好旺㗎喎！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係囉，呢排都麻煩，靜咗好多。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：嘩，上次好亂喎！好彩星期日啲差人無走入嚟，嚇死呀！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係呀！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：就喺你地對面咋喎上次換衫班人！好彩啲差人無放催淚煙呀！嘩啲煙吹埋嚟，你啲嘢唔要得㗎啦！點賣畀人呀？啲煙有毒㗎喎！新聞都有報呀！<br />\n嘩真係好彩呀！食死人點算呀？都唔知告邊個！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：。。。唉！係囉！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住我就走了。從老闆同老闆娘反應可見，其實佢諗都冇諗過啲煙會搞到自己間鋪。<br />\n<br />\n小妹覺得呢招植入式不妨一試。等班自以為係既得利益者知道差人會令佢地蒙受巨大的損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696cfe74ad9fe3a980e0f339b8a4406dea0af848","tid":1473143,"uid":44747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T22:53:11.000Z","msg":"我可唔可以丟絲打個鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795fed3465c51b4e2e5fc4fd8548b3d648e5f926","tid":1473143,"uid":212217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T22:53:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>求推求推! 香港人可以試下「節奏抗爭」noise making protest! </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[推膠招]全民係屋企都可以示威:Noise-Making抗爭法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469010</a>"},{"pid":"510856966deb9db6560fa0066c257995ec193c97","tid":1473143,"uid":287107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}